_sText:
My First Map

Thanks to the Incredible: Chizbone  for tuning my nav mesh
(he is also the nav_editor of cs_atafaris+ ,de_phoenix_steel and de_cityfever)


For both teams are two spawn/startpoints added to make the game more interesting and not repeating itself round for round for round.
So its more tactic and random start-standups for each team.


Please note, that you can support your team from both bombspots while planting/defusing the bomb!!!

There are several ways between the bombspots to increase the gameflow, underground and overground (at the rooftops) + you have an advantage while shooting from the roof!
